import {
	addNewPlayer,
	deletePlayer,
	getPlayers,
	getPlayerWithId,
	updatePlayer,
} from "../controllers/playerControllers"

const routes = (app) => {
	app.route("/players")
    .get(getPlayers)
    .post(addNewPlayer)

	app
		.route("/player:PlayerId")
		.get(getPlayerWithId)
		.put(updatePlayer)
		.delete(deletePlayer)
}

export default routes
